</div><br />
</div>


<p></p></p>

<p>In addition, if you'd like to get hands-on experience with a number of techniques to make your Drupal site perform like a champion, I'm honored to be co-presenting the <a href="http://denver2012.drupal.org/content/drupal-performance-and-scalability">Drupal Performance and Scalability training</a> alongside <a href="http://denver2012.drupal.org/users/msonnabaum">Mark Sonnabaum from Acquia</a> and <a href="http://drupal.org/user/35821">Nate Haug from Lullabot</a>!</p>


<p></p></p>

<p>See you in Denver, and until then, Varnish <u>all</u> the things!</p>


